4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior experience, aiming to build foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration. Participants will learn key concepts in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Upon completion, students earn an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes can be conducted in English or Spanish, depending on the campus. For more details, please visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop